      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WIRRULLA HARRY (2) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 2.5 lengths at this track in a handy 19.91 beating Antecedent. Great chance again. CHARLIE'S HARLEY (8) jumped from this same draw and was close to the lead throughout before boxing on well and holding a 6 length third (20.12) at this track over 342m in a Special conditions race. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. This tougher but expected to be in the finish. WAIT AND SEE (1) has shown decent speed at his last couple and filled minor placings, last time finishing second beaten 4.5 lengths (20.01). Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Hard to beat again. BUDGEREE (5) won as expected last time – cannot be taken lightly.",
